description: Demolition of the existing buildings around the Victorian printworks T-block building, retention of and alterations to the listed building at 135 Clapham Road, retention of the Victorian printworks building and erection of new buildings varying in height (maximum six storeys) containing 260 residential units, retail (Class A1), financial and professional services (Class A2), restaurants and cafe's (Class A3), drinking establishments (Class A4), and business (Class B1), with provision of 140 car parking spaces, cycle parking and associated landscaping. DEPARTURE FROM DEVELOPMENT PLAN.
